{"tid":1689020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想提返前線","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T14:32:20.000Z","uid":220900,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee963bcd4f8dcc4611c961340222b446529eb75","tid":1689020,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"對峙嘅時候一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">捉實身邊手足，捉實身邊手足，捉實身邊手足</span></strong></span>（重要野要講3次），捉背囊應該係最方便（？）<br />\n<br />\n如圖所示<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbP5WqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbP5WqX.png&h=5e5f16fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pw0AzcF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw0AzcF.png&h=6d53e62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實之前大家好有呢個意識，71爆立會嗰陣同班狗只係一玻璃之隔，大家捉到對方實一實，係會相對安全，至少手足冇咁易俾人拖走。<br />\n<br />\n但最近真係好少見到有人有意識咁做，就算係現場點叫都好，都係得幾個人會跟住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔知係大家覺得捉住冇用定點，但其實<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>呢個咁簡單嘅動作，係可以防止到手足落單，可以減少班狗突然單拖衝前拖走手足，甚至可以俾前面嘅人知道自己身後仲有冇人</strong></span></span>，大家依家成日話要救人，但預防勝於治療，捉實手足，防止手足落單都好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同嘅麻煩幫手推一推，希望下次出去，前線全部都自覺性地捉實手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，反抗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8c2ad5474d86054064debceaccd354e0735c4d53","tid":1689020,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d55fc1d58e3c48b259426ed621