","tid":1689020,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7eda231a2b61c37bdf9eae744ad82e8837aebd44","tid":1689020,"uid":173844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"傳開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉背囊！齊上齊落"},{"pid":"34dce6e8fb141a3e1380b527750582d47ba67706","tid":1689020,"uid":49560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:19:23.000Z","msg":"TUI"},{"pid":"043abceaaace6a8c9c81b2dd532eae3b5996e04a","tid":1689020,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee963bcd4f8dcc4611c961340222b446529eb75","tid":1689020,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"對峙嘅時候一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">捉實身邊手足，捉實身邊手足，捉實身邊手足</span></strong></span>（重要野要講3次），捉背囊應該係最方便（？）<br />\n<br />\n如圖所示<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbP5WqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbP5WqX.png&h=5e5f16fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pw0AzcF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw0AzcF.png&h=6d53e62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實之前大家好有呢個意識，71爆立會嗰陣同班狗只係一玻璃之隔，大家捉到對方實一實，係會相對安全，至少手足冇咁易俾人拖走。<br />\n<br />\n但最近真係好少見到有人有意識咁做，就算係現場點叫都好，都係得幾個人會跟住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔知係大家覺得捉住冇用定點，但其實<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>呢個咁簡單嘅動作，係可以防止到手足落單，可以減少班狗突然單拖衝前拖走手足，甚至可以俾前面嘅人知道自己身後仲有冇人</strong></span></span>，大家依家成日話要救人，但預防勝於治療，捉實手足，防止手足落單都好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同嘅麻煩幫手推一推，希望下次出去，前線全部都自覺性地捉實手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，反抗</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"推，但我覺得主因係恐慌性咁走，比哂個背班狗打，人人只顧自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係指責，驚係人之常情，講真今時今日仲敢着件黑衫岀來行已經要有勇氣。希望可以再進一步"},{"pid":"676ded1b595d83f0b692088773d22e99e5912ace","tid":1689020,"uid":47710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a8e8961476f8a8e7a5b90b330580b5c357ac16a","tid":1689020,"uid":65831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"我開post叫人唔好掉頭走，捉住前面個手捉倒後行，俾人屌話想仆死啲手捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313f60feed3baf47af407ed9169986fd5d34b646","tid":1689020,"uid":220900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"043abceaaace6a8c9c81b2dd532eae3b5996e04a","tid":1689020,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee963bcd4f8dcc4611c961340222b446529eb75","tid":1689020,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"對峙嘅時候一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">捉實身邊手足，捉實身邊手足，捉實身邊手足</span></strong></span>（重要野要講3次），捉背囊應該係最方便（？）<br />\n<br />\n如圖所示<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbP5WqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbP5WqX.png&h=5e5f16fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pw0AzcF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw0AzcF.png&h=6d53e62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實之前大家好有呢個意識，71爆立會嗰陣同班狗只係一玻璃之隔，大家捉到對方實一實，係會相對安全，至少手足冇咁易俾人拖走。<br />\n<br />\n但最近真係好少見到有人有意識咁做，就算係現場點叫都好，都係得幾個人會跟住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔知係大家覺得捉住冇用定點，但其實<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>呢個咁簡單嘅動作，係可以防止到手足落單，可以減少班狗突然單拖衝前拖走手足，甚至可以俾前面嘅人知道自己身後仲有冇人</strong></span></span>，大家依家成日話要救人，但預防勝於治療，捉實手足，防止手足落單都好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同嘅麻煩幫手推一推，希望下次出去，前線全部都自覺性地捉實手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，反抗</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"推，但我覺得主因係恐慌性咁走，比哂個背班狗打，人人只顧自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係指責，驚係人之常情，講真今時今日仲敢着件黑衫岀來行已經要有勇氣。希望可以再進一步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"認同恐慌性咁走係主因，依家眼見可以保持冷靜嘅手足真係愈黎愈少，而恐慌性咁走，最大問題係會令夠膽留低、識慢慢退嘅手足都要即刻跑走，所以我先覺得捉書包真係好緊要，要俾前線知道自己後面係退緊定守緊，保持前線上落一致，另外新手前線都可能會因為有人捉住而定啲<br />\n<br />\n走到呢步，同你一樣，已經唔會再指責人跑走，屌黎屌去對件事真係冇幫助，反而真心希望大家可以一齊諗到啲方便去改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bff270cb33a993ddfb6a80bd1e538e9a32e72af","tid":1689020,"uid":249162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>哩點好緊要！</strong></span></span>仲有某程度上比左個安全感對方，比對方知有support"},{"pid":"8337e7c53b8f051ca456de83503ade922d323e3e","tid":1689020,"uid":336913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"希望有bug令我推到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5241e99890c4eba3c7d7b1236c87d49f56ae1b6f","tid":1689020,"uid":113800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"57db92c00a77ade8edc958388eb4e63065ef42d1","tid":1689020,"uid":113800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"5c4e915adfde1d1cdc06b2e96b60ad7775e57724","tid":1689020,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"7a07271da2a5bfce7f01c47248f8fb8ec34361d4","tid":1689020,"uid":148795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n根本唔使1212咁跑走<br />\n成班人面向班狗慢慢向後退反而班狗唔敢衝入人群<br />\n因為知個位人口密度太高 好易激到其他人反打班狗<br />\n相反向後跑班狗就知㩒低完你都唔會有其他人救"},{"pid":"a0761086191aad356870db8e27ea232a5d386e51","tid":1689020,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"b70a34927fa954ac318ed1dfefa44c1d070741a4","tid":1689020,"uid":160447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:53:27.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2a6991f91da33983e5722ca2735eb4964e26de25","tid":1689020,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"第二張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611551ce26d1949d9b6bccfb380a6706311f4222","tid":1689020,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6991f91da33983e5722ca2735eb4964e26de25","tid":1689020,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"第二張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/